OL,3,CAssaulting shop workers to become
OL,4,Cspecific offence in new legislation
OL,6,FA few months ago ministers said it
OL,7,Fwasn't necessary, but now the
OL,8,Fgovernment has made assaulting
OL,9,Fshopworkers a specific offence after a
OL,10,Fspike in violent attacks. ITV News
OL,11,FPolitical Correspondent Harry Horton
OL,12,Freports
OL,14,FAssaulting a shopworker is going to be
OL,15,Fmade its own criminal offence after
OL,16,Fthe government has rowed back on its
OL,17,Fprevious position following a long-
OL,18,Frunning campaign.
