OL,3,CAssaulting shop workers to become
OL,4,Cspecific offence in new legislation
OL,6,FMinisters had previously ruled out
OL,7,Flegislating to create a new offence,
OL,8,Fsaying in response to a parliamentary
OL,9,Fpetition in October they did not think
OL,10,Fit was "required or will be most
OL,11,Feffective".
OL,13,FBut on Wednesday, Prime Minister Rishi
OL,14,FSunak announced that his government
OL,15,Fwill be amending its Criminal Justice
OL,16,FBill to bring in the new offence,
OL,17,Fwhich will apply to England and Wales.
