OL,3,CAssaulting shop workers to become
OL,4,Cspecific offence in new legislation
OL,6,FThe new offence will carry a maximum
OL,7,Fsentence of six months' imprisonment
OL,8,For an unlimited fine, the same
OL,9,Fsentence for the existing offence of
OL,10,Fcommon assault.
OL,12,FRepeat offenders could also be forced
OL,13,Fto wear an electronic tag, as could
OL,14,Fconsistent , under amendments to the
OL,15,FBill currently making its way through
OL,16,FParliament.
