OL,3,CAssaulting shop workers to become
OL,4,Cspecific offence in new legislation
OL,6,FEarlier this year, the British Retail
OL,7,FConsortium (BRC) published a report
OL,8,Fsaying violent and abusive incidents
OL,9,Fagainst shopworkers had increased 50%
OL,10,Fbetween 2021/22 and 2022/23.
OL,12,FHelen Dickinson, chairwoman of the
OL,13,FBRC, welcomed the announcement, saying
OL,14,Fthat "the voices of the three million
OL,15,Fpeople working in retail are finally
OL,16,Fbeing heard".
